{"tid":986712,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個另一半令你進步嘅故事","createTime":"2019-01-18T16:36:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T16:37:23.000Z","uid":134997,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab9268ff37ac4f529123b6fcb81100e93ffea80","tid":986712,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:36:04.000Z","msg":"前兩三年考dse study leave嗰陣<br />\n諗住棄左chem溫bio同phy算<br />\n佢叫我應承佢唔好放棄任何一科<br />\n結果我兩個月study leave淨係溫chem一科<br />\n結果chem啱啱好5** 入左hku<br />\n<br />\n中三嗰陣試過臨選港隊前一個禮拜<br />\n（唔講咩波驚自爆）<br />\n斷撚左十字韌帶<br />\n我喊撚到想死 話一世唔再打波<br />\n又係佢安慰我 叫我努力唔好放棄<br />\n休息左年半 再開始打返波<br />\n結果中六嗰年用隊長身分<br />\n攞左次學屆冠軍<br />\n<br />\n所以有個好嘅另一半 一齊進步<br />\n真係好重要<br />\n我愛你呀女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fc71ab7583b67e48217095536088d65d64f809","tid":986712,"uid":134997,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:37:13.000Z","msg":"我屌你老味邊個睇都未睇就負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6603bb371120f3876bd84691dca81c69cabc5a52","tid":986712,"uid":226562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T16:37:23.000Z","msg":"留名"}]}